      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must have documented V&V test suite with regression tracking and release notes for each build. Configuration management records must trace each simulation to a specific software build.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS CFX 15.0 has a documented QA test suite; however, configuration management records for the 2026-q1-build-7 release are incomplete. Only the 2024-q3-build-2 build has full regression logs available. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
