      "rationale": "FDA PIV dataset uses glycerol-water analog; no biological sample characterization applicable. In-vitro hemolysis measurements from Morrison et al. do not report donor RBC characterization or osmotic fragility. Sample variability not quantified. Not assessed at MRL 5. Achieved level 1."
