      "rationale": "Reynolds number matching attempted between glycerol-water experiments and blood simulations but Womersley number and hematocrit effects not addressed. No formal equivalency documentation produced. Critical gap for absolute hemolysis prediction at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
